{"tid":166335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗警署車長 昏迷警車內不治","createTime":"2017-03-22T04:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T06:52:44.000Z","uid":28435,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6256f0b3658f4c6a8a9f38cfeb58ec37bf55cd","tid":166335,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9k6QhV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9k6QhV.jpg&h=b4201512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗警署一名男警，今晨8時被發現昏迷不醒。救護員接報到場，將警員送到明愛醫院搶救，但證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者為負責駕駛警車的車長，警員編號59137，被同袍暱稱「細龜」。昨晚他返夜更，當時曾表示身體不適，今早收工後登上俗稱「大車」的警車上休息，直至早上8時，另一名車長要用車，載同袍往燒槍訓練，卻發現細龜昏迷車內，於是召救護車將他送院，惜返魂乏術，死者留下妻子及一對子女。"},{"pid":"57743cc1126001a48f6e85b3c85bcde5c2d97e42","tid":166335,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d4ffef31339e71c781dd188604e81e811c536a","tid":166335,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"要唔要請小鳳姐？"},{"pid":"021724316586999f59647553f97ed97c7149168b","tid":166335,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"fb197b04f620218276ff8608841d685606709d04","tid":166335,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d878e4ea3a1cb060749b7f8bda1a2f5355e2e2a","tid":166335,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"死得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a4a6b16c10e720a429d6e14bca9c3e087d3789","tid":166335,"uid":34640,"like":0,"dislike":0,